        <tls:srcline title="祖堂集" target="#KR6q0002_Yan_005-2002a.1" pos="">「當是天
                        龍八部、釋梵助化之光。」</tls:srcline>
        <tls:line title="祖堂集 (en)">"It was certainly the light of the eight kinds of heavenly beings and dragon kings, Indra and Brahma who assisst in teaching [the Buddha-dharma]."</tls:line>
